## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of sources reviewed. The findings are based on articles and reports that may not cover all aspects of the issue comprehensively. Additionally, the report focuses on specific regions, which may not fully represent global trends. Further research with more recent data and broader geographic coverage would provide a more complete picture of the factors influencing crime rates.